reviews.reviewText: This thing is plastic, not diecast. Came with a bag with elephants on them for some reasonOnly giving this two stars, because at the very least my brother thinks it's OK and the bag was a nice little gift to mom, though he's pretty disappointed. I'm disappointed that I had to pay the price i did for something so small and not even a collectable.I'll leave it be, though. Just gonna have to get something elsewhere.
